name: "When Life Gives You Lemons..." by RFY (HF) & FEH
description:
[Crayon and jewel collage on colored cardstock with digital embellishments and color.] Another classic collaboration with my granddaughter, Felicity. I drew the head, she drew the eyes, and I added the jewels, then I sent the whole shebang to the DIGITAL PROCESSING LABORATORY for the finishing touches! Looked like a Lemon-Head monster to me, once we were done!

---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson (Holy Toddler)
